replies.body:
Ok I have 2 for my baby {{champion:111}} 

1. if you E then Q while near the enemy you can hit them with multiple E ripples.

1. if you attack and then quickly use W your auto will reset and you will attack 2 times very quickly.

{{champion:86}} 
can use all his abilities during E without interupting E except his ult which will cancel E.

E cannot be stopped by any CC (you will still stop moving though) and will spin till the end of its duration this litle gimick is why garen can counter the crap out of {{champion:92}} 
and use decisive strike during E for increased movement speed and instant silence to counter your slows from E.
and activate W only when riven or anyone else is going ham right before, so you reduce their damage by 30% while they CANNOT stop your onslaught.

congratz now even the so called garen counters will have to be on their toes or still horribly lose lane
